        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 25 at 3:44PM MDT until June 25 at 4:45PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>SVRGGW

The National Weather Service in Glasgow has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
East central Garfield County in northeastern Montana...
West central McCone County in northeastern Montana...

* Until 445 PM MDT.

* At 344 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 9 miles west of
Nelson Creek Rec Area, or 28 miles northeast of Jordan, moving east
at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Nelson Creek Rec Area and Rock Creek Rec Area.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
